title: Lexus / Toyota EU 2008-2009 ver.1 Navigation DVD North Europe
description:
This is:	PZ485-X03EU-08 2008-2009 Ver.1.
86807-0W062 <- Enter this number to http://www.toyota-mapupdates.eu/ or to   <a href="
http://www.lexus-mapupdates.eu/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.lexus-mapupdates.eu/</a> if you want check for updates of this product

You can use this sofware, if your navi works with the following software:
86271-53030 (86271-60V660E) 2005-2006 Ver.1
86271-53031 (86271-60V661A) 2006-2007 Ver.2
86807-0W050                 2007-2008 Russia
86807-0W060                 2007-2008 Ver.1
86807-0W061                 2007-2008 Ver.2

Burn onto a DVD+R DL in DVD-ROM mode at 2.4x speed or will NOT work !
Verbatim is preferred, altough other medias also working (e.g. TDK).


DVD Part numbers:
86271-0W081, 86271-60W381, E11 Europe North 

DVD Europe North coverage:
Austria, Belgium, Switzerland, Czech republic, Germany, Denmark,
Finland, Liechtenstein, Luxembourg, Norway, Netherlands, Poland,
Sweden, Slovak Republic, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania


This DVD has been modified! One file has been replaced by an older (E10) version:
LOADING.KWI has been replaced from the E10 version, so it will not check if you use OTP or PTP discs.
The only disadvantage: the block for the operation of the navigation during driving is still disabled. It is enabled from E11 version upwards but for only users with original DVDs.

The modification on the DVD was done with UltraISO (v9.3.3.2685), in the Configuration menu under Save tab, everything has to be turned off! (Recompile ISO, Enable Super Restore, etc.)
